summary: I haven’t really talked about this, but when I saw that Phil was in the hospital (and after him saying that he was ok) I didn’t...
body:
I haven’t really talked about this, but when I saw that Phil was in the hospital (and after him saying that he was ok) I didn’t give it much thought, but then, Phil posted the story of Dan with him in the hospital room and I realized something stupid and that I already knew

They are a couple, they not only live together but they care about each other

Taking your significant other to the hospital in case of need and staying with them the entire time is one of the purest form of love (maybe I’m exaggerating this a bit but I’m emotional let me live)

And I realized how much they love each other and I just started crying in class idk
